videos.description: LB Pat Jasinski picks off FAU QB Chris Robison to set up a touchdown drive for the Knights.
videos.headline: UCF comes away with INT on first drive of game

videos.description: McKenzie Milton keeps it himself on the quarterback run to give the Knights an early 7-0 lead on FAU.
videos.headline: UCF takes lead on 12-yard QB keeper

videos.description: UCF QB McKenzie Milton finds WR Dredrick Snelson in the back of the end zone, making it 14-0 Knights.
videos.headline: Milton throws dime for 12-yard TD

videos.description: RB Gerald Hearns takes the direct snap in punt formation and runs for 24 yards, setting up an Owls touchdown.
videos.headline: FAU executes fake punt to perfection

videos.description: RB Devin Singletary bulldozes his way into the end zone, cutting the UCF lead in half to 14-7.
videos.headline: FAU gets on board with 11-yard TD run

videos.description: FAU RB Devin Singletary sheds a tackle and scores on a 9-yard touchdown run, knotting the game at 14-14.
videos.headline: Singletary ties game with 2nd TD of quarter

videos.description: QB McKenzie Milton hits a wide open Marlon Williams, who takes it to the end zone and makes it 21-17 Knights before halftime.
videos.headline: UCF reclaims lead with 21-yard TD pass

videos.description: UCF QB McKenzie Milton finds paydirt on a 9-yard quarterback run, extending the Knights' lead to 28-17.
videos.headline: Milton scores his 2nd rush TD of game

videos.description: QB Chris Robison swings it to RB Kerrith White Jr., who escapes the defense and scores to make it 35-23 UCF.
videos.headline: FAU responds with 23-yard TD pass

videos.description: QB McKenzie Milton throws a strike to WR Gabriel Davis, who takes it across the goal-line and gives the Knights a 42-23 lead.
videos.headline: UCF offense stays hot with 19-yard TD pass

videos.description: LB Eric Mitchell picks off FAU QB Chris Robison to give the Knights possession before the end of the 3rd quarter.
videos.headline: UCF defense comes up with 2nd INT of game

videos.description: RB Devin Singletary finds an opening and gets to the end zone, narrowing the Knights' lead to 42-29.
videos.headline: FAU hangs around with 5-yard rush TD

videos.description: RB Taj McGowan busts through the defense and scores to make it 49-29 late in the 4th quarter.
videos.headline: UCF ices game with 6-yard TD run
